$:/plugins/oeyoews/tiddlywiki-fancybox/r.title: $:/plugins/oeyoews/tiddlywiki-fancybox/readme
$:/plugins/oeyoews/tiddlywiki-fancybox/r.text:
!! Readme

<!-- * 只需要安装此插件即可， 无需额外配置， 自动识别图片tiddlywiki当前界面(不是所有)的所有图片, -->
<!-- 点击即可放大图片(如果不起作用, 请刷新tiddlywiki使用)， -->
`Updated Time:  2023-01-09 20:02:49+0800`
 <!-- 后期更新说明请点击 [[readme|https://oeyoewl.top/fancybox-gallery-tiddlywiki]] -->

* [[Demo|https://neotw.netlify.app/main.html#%24%3A%2Fplugins%2Foeyoews%2Ftiddlywiki-fancybox]]

* [[Source|https://github.com/oeyoews/neotw/tree/main/dev/plugins/tiddlywiki-fancybox]]

* [[Tiddlyhost site|https://fancybox-oeyoews.tiddlyhost.com]]

!! Features

* support download images, fullscreen, custom style and shortcuts,
<!-- !! Note -->
<!-- * 由于是动态给img加上一个父标签, -->
<!-- 只会渲染启动时识别到的img标签，如果导入新的图片或者打开新的含有图片的tiddler, -->
<!-- 则需要重新刷新当前界面，让插件重新渲染DOM -->
<!-- * how to add refresh tip on tiddlywiki js?? -->

!! Usage

<!-- !!! 分组 -->
<!-- * 如果一个tiddler 中的图片来自多个其他的tiddler, 则会展示多个tid的图片分组, -->
<!-- 如果当前tiddler的图片全部来自单个tiddler则会只会展示一个图片分组(此功能目前借助<<qualify>> -->
<!-- 宏实现) -->
{{$:/plugins/oeyoews/tiddlywiki-fancybox/example}}

!! Links

* fancybox: https://github.com/fancyapps/fancybox

!! Note

* if you use splashscreen, please remove `remove-when-wiki-loaded` class,
otherwise this plugin will not work normally [[warn|https://github.com/Jermolene/TiddlyWiki5/search?q=tc-remove-when-wiki-loaded]]
* not support local svg at least

!! TODO

* use widget or js macro instead macro

<!-- no jq -->
<!-- just for local temporary, render again -->
`<script>
      const lables = document.querySelectorAll("img");
      const elem = document.createElement("a");
      lables.forEach((lable, index) => {
        const elem = document.createElement("a");
        elem.href = lable.getAttribute("src")
        elem.setAttribute("data-fancybox", "gallary");
        lable.parentNode.replaceChild(elem, lable);
        elem.appendChild(lable);
      });`
`</script>`

$:/plugins/oeyoews/tiddlywiki-fancybox/c.title: $:/plugins/oeyoews/tiddlywiki-fancybox/config
$:/plugins/oeyoews/tiddlywiki-fancybox/c.text:
\define tid() $:/plugins/oeyoews/tiddlywiki-fancybox/init
\define tid-msg() $:/plugins/oeyoews/tiddlywiki-fancybox/msg
\define tag() $:/tags/RawMarkupWikified/BottomBody
\define mode() $:/status/tiddlywiki-fancybox/mode

<!-- one config -->
<$list filter=<<mode>> variable=".state">

  <!-- add  -->
  <$reveal state=<<.state>> type="nomatch" text="hide">
    <$fieldmangler tiddler=<<tid>> >
      <$button set=<<.state>> setTo="hide">Enable Fancybox Global {{neotw/icon/approve}}
        <$action-sendmessage $message="tm-add-tag" $param=<<tag>>/>
        <$action-sendmessage $message="tm-notify" $param=<<tid-msg>>/>
      </$button>
    </$fieldmangler>
  </$reveal>

  <!-- remove -->
  <$reveal state=<<.state>> type="match" text="hide">
    <$fieldmangler tiddler=<<tid>> >
      <$button set=<<.state>> setTo="show">Disable Fancybox Global {{neotw/icon/warn}}
        <$action-sendmessage $message="tm-remove-tag" $param=<<tag>>/>
        <$action-sendmessage $message="tm-notify" $param=<<tid-msg>>/>
      </$button>
    </$fieldmangler>
  </$reveal>

</$list>
